<p>Since you mentioned that we cannot change the standard deviations of odometry because it is part of the process model, I wonder: if we add odometry data with variable standard deviations to a pose estimator fed with an empty position/swerve module states (as the process model), as if we were adding vision measurements, wouldn’t we achieve the desired result?</p>
